details: This filter performed flawlessly during our harsh winter. Even at -20°F, no leaks or pressure issues. Best cold weather filter I've used.
The filtration quality is exceptional. My oil stays cleaner longer between changes. Engine runs smoother too.
It's an adequate filter that does what it's supposed to do. Nothing exceptional but no issues either.
Living in Minnesota, I need a filter that can handle extreme cold. This one excels - no leaks or pressure issues even at -30°F.

It's a good filter but I'm not sure it's worth the premium price. Performance is only slightly better than standard filters.

Performance is average. I don't see a significant difference compared to standard filters.
